{"tid":395843,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"井上尚彌作客美國KO東道主拳手 6度衛冕金腰帶兼14連勝","createTime":"2017-09-11T07:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T09:44:19.000Z","uid":9030,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9564bac7974eb657892e1ca5f14ce216f8cbc68e","tid":395843,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"外號「怪物」的井上尚彌是日本拳壇新星，年僅24歲已在世界拳壇享負盛名。井上尚彌更是目前WBO超蠅量級世界拳王，被視為同樣是超蠅量級的香港「神奇小子」曹星如終極目標。日前（9月9日）井上尚彌到美國加州出戰首場海外對決，第6度力爭衛冕超蠅量級「金腰帶」，挑戰者為東道主拳手利維斯（Antonio Nieves）。<br />\n<br />\n兩人原定進行12回合激戰，惟世界排名第7的利維斯在第5回合被井上尚彌打倒在地上，僅支撐6個回合便由場邊助手「扔毛巾」棄權，要求拳證終止比賽，井上尚彌宣布生涯第6度衛冕WBO超蠅量級世界拳王成功，職業生涯14連勝。賽後井上尚彌指出：「我對自己的表現很滿意，他（利維斯）是一個勇敢的鬥士，但今晚，我對他來說太強了。」"},{"pid":"027b9ea56011f7d2a5db1027a6c2bf6452c88d59","tid":395843,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:29:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/91BBcLF-UU4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F91BBcLF-UU4&d=zm1YLSEXK%2Bh7fiA9yBSUQZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=de8eaa9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/91BBcLF-UU4</a>"},{"pid":"98f90341d661f700eb09b09e4c48833b55591fdc","tid":395843,"uid":82304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚勁"},{"pid":"bb2f3de762c329ee0921ef6e6a8c7d9295d3c0c7","tid":395843,"uid":9030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"Antonio Nieves WBO排名No.7, 挑戰井上尚彌<br />\nRex Tso現時排名No.2, 最高排名No.1, 未曾挑戰井上尚彌"},{"pid":"4356c65008ba494d06dec0b540818467ef17099a","tid":395843,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚勁</blockquote><br />\n人地24一路一路成熟, 相反rex tso已經3張, 越遲打越冇得打"},{"pid":"4434bec0ac365f5acd8d7fd5b2658f3b79b7c2c7","tid":395843,"uid":82304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚勁</blockquote><br />\n人地24一路一路成熟, 相反rex tso已經3張, 越遲打越冇得打</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0877bbf98af787498d5a5c81d6999faa7403ee48","tid":395843,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"拳重完全唔係同一個檔次，唔駛幻想佢地會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417adb65058483db8e557df36652a9ecccb00e2b","tid":395843,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:07:53.000Z","msg":"好廢，tyson應該一拳打柒日本仔"},{"pid":"a1c7767afeef51f9b898be21b600eaa3128c0dd9","tid":395843,"uid":82304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:11:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拳重完全唔係同一個檔次，唔駛幻想佢地會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes 跟本輸硬"},{"pid":"09a072b90769763143665d3b6904fb0ef9dbaa66","tid":395843,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好廢，tyson應該一拳打柒日本仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世清一拳打死佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3aafedeb28398daf94071b58b4574ef99b9f70","tid":395843,"uid":142819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"rex tso 幾時同人打返場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b427f2f41de4bd6da8e21d2eb04b732ef0442d","tid":395843,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:41:13.000Z","msg":"勁撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f44fe8334454d27a34ae0b6de4721885774c2f","tid":395843,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09